  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We can speculate that the best responders to tocilizumab should have multiple related
      elements (Treg CD39, adenosine, IL-35) successfully induced and expressed in order to play
      its beneficial role. The study of these elements and its pathways could help identify the
      best responders to tocilizumab treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
