    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients of all sexes, aged ≥ 18 years.

          -  RA Patients (according to ACR / EULAR criteria 2010) of moderate to severe activity
             (DAS 28&gt; 3.2 or SDAI&gt; 11), and 6 months or more of evolution, starting treatment with
             ACTEMRA (tocilizumab) or with an anti-TNF, according to the product data.

          -  Patients with body weight ≤ 150 kg.

          -  Patients who have received written information about the study and gave their informed
             consent to participate in the study

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with a history of autoimmune disease or inflammatory joint disease other than
             RA.

          -  Patients treated with any investigational agent within 4 weeks (or 5 half-lives of
             investigational agent, whichever is greater) before starting treatment with
             tocilizumab
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
